            "title": "滬指開市升27點 深成指重越萬四關開升242點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">人大會議今早開幕，疊加外圍股市反彈，內地股市今早初段亦回升。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/20260303_FI_source-ap_ChinaEco-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/20260303_FI_source-ap_ChinaEco-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">上證綜指以4109點開市，升27點或0.67%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">深證成指開市已重越14000點，開報14160點，升242點或1.74%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滬深300指數升49點或1.07%，開報4651點；創業板指數開市報3236點，升71點或2.27%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15708256-%e6%bb%ac%e6%8c%87%e9%96%8b%e5%b8%82%e5%8d%8727%e9%bb%9e-%e6%b7%b1%e6%88%90%e6%8c%87%e9%87%8d%e8%b6%8a%e8%90%ac%e5%9b%9b%e9%97%9c%e9%96%8b%e5%8d%87242%e9%bb%9e",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-14.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-05 09:31:52",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
