            "title": "港股開市︱初段反彈 恒指回升334點報25583點 京東績前高開近1%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">外圍股市反彈，港股今早同樣高開。恒生指數開市報25583點，升334點或1.32%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒生科技指數開報4907點，升77點或1.61%；國企指數以8577點開市，升93點或1.1%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_HKEX_FB.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_HKEX_FB.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">重磅股普遍回升，滙控(00005)ADR昨晚已回升至折合每股136.3元，反彈4.2%，該股今早亦高開2.98%，報134.7元。將於今日收市後派成績表的京東(09618)，今早以98.95元開市，升0.97%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">其他重磅科股方面，阿里巴巴(09988)開報130.5元，升0.46%；騰訊(00700)開報509.5元，升0.69%；美團(03690)開報76.65元，升1.66%；小米(01810)開報32.56元，升1.75%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：京東官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/12/20251230_FI_source-web_09618.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：京東官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/12/20251230_FI_source-web_09618.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：京東官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">中國秦發(00866)今早訂立配股協議，擬折讓10%配股籌3.16億元；該股今早開報3.87元，跌0.77%；多牛科技(01961)折讓14.75%配股，該股今早不跌反升，以0.35元開市，彈14.75%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15708240-%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e9%96%8b%e5%b8%82%ef%b8%b1%e5%88%9d%e6%ae%b5%e5%8f%8d%e5%bd%88-%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e5%9b%9e%e5%8d%87334%e9%bb%9e%e5%a0%b125583%e9%bb%9e-%e4%ba%ac%e6%9d%b1%e7%b8%be%e5%89%8d%e9%ab%98",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/HKSTOCK.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-05 09:31:52",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
